OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a dry day and cloudy
OL,6,Fat times but still with some good
OL,7,Fbright and sunny spells, the best of
OL,8,Fthese will be early morning and again
OL,9,Ffrom late afternoon. Light
OL,10,Fnorthwesterly winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FIt will be a dry evening with
OL,13,Fcloud breaking up to give some late
OL,14,Fsunny spells. Remaining dry overnight
OL,15,Fwith clear spells and light winds.
OL,16,
OL,17,CMonday:FA few mist and fog patches
OL,18,Fwhich will be quick to clear in the
OL,19,Fmorning to leave a dry and settled day
OL,20,Fwith light winds and plenty sunny
OL,21,Fspells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
