OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FMostly
OL,6,Fcloudy on Tuesday with a few showers
OL,7,Fpossible. High pressure bringing dry
OL,8,Fand settled conditions with light
OL,9,Fwinds and plenty of sunny spells on
OL,10,FWednesday and Thursday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
